comment.body:
Hi! The `decoder` must extend the `EventEmitter` class:

```js
const Emitter = require("component-emitter"); // polyfill of Node.js EventEmitter in the browser 

class Decoder extends Emitter {
  // ...
}

module.exports = { Encoder, Decoder };
```

That being said, we could totally provide an abstract decoder that users would extend.

